included.description:
UX researcher for the Search Engagement Team. Conducted independent research studies to help create better designs & better the designs already created. Worked with PMs, Designers & engineers to create User centered designs. 
Conducted lab studies, cafe studies to understand users better & gain feedback on the product created. By means of secondary research & analysis helped create newer ideas that could be integrated into the product.
included.title: User Experience Researcher

included.description:
A 10-week, full time UX Design career accelerator course focusing on User-centered design solutions, User research, Ideation & User testing along with emphasis on rapid prototyping, Lean UX and collaborative design thinking.

Projects:

Brightwheel app

Role: UX Designer & Researcher

-Presented a new & improved brightwheel app design based upon user interviews, testing new prototypes & client feedback, over a period of 3-weeks. 


Mind Magic app

Role: UX Designer & Researcher 

-Collaboratively worked on researching and designing a app for a medical alert system to reduce the reluctance in their subscribers to use the service. Created an app as an extension of the service to keep family members updated of the subscribers mental wellbeing by users playing games to meet goals related to mental acumen and alertness.


Progress Hardware Website

-Designed a e-commerce site for a privately owned local hardware store while keeping its values of service and community feel intact. 


Fun For All App

-Created an app through rapid prototyping and hand sketching to help young families decide on local family activities for the weekend.
